{"tid":1623554,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(四两撥千斤)利用政府幫香港三罷","createTime":"2019-10-04T23:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T02:16:13.000Z","uid":146508,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1d75348ce1304cad241fea11c3d54d3879ec1f67","tid":1623554,"uid":146508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:45:04.000Z","msg":"過左琴晚，政府呢幾日既戰略好明顯。<br />\n<br />\n星期五好趕地立《禁蒙面法》，<br />\n目的係用星期五六日一，結束呢場示威，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界星期二恢復正常，返工返學</span><br />\n<br />\n點結束？對方估到一立法我地實嬲到仆街，並利用我地既憤怒<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1：呢幾日利用埋條蒙面法，再封埋鐵，大圍捕捉大量前線，等你地唔敢再出</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2:搵臥底爆金舖，打家劫舍，屈落示威者度，令我地失民意失國際支持</span><br />\n<br />\n而我地要做既野非常簡單。簡單來說拖長佢對我地非常有利<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1：堅守不被捕原則<br />\n唔係叫你唔好走，而真係唔好戀戰<br />\n留返條命同佢下星期二三四先慢慢玩<br />\n佢今日咁都封全港黨鐵<br />\n有本事一直封落去，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港最大支援三罷既助力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n撐到佢下星期要繼續封鐵，<br />\n大量返工返學既手足因此而可以閒日都同佢玩<br />\n真係諗到都開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">2：堅守&ldquo;核彈都唔割&ldquo;<br />\n唔好咁易俾風向狗帶到好無？<br />\n俾多少少信任前線<br />\n另外隔離post講得好啱<br />\n即使有時做多左<br />\n都要&ldquo;先唔割，後補救&ldquo;<br />\n另外你諗下，啲狗同狗官同黨鐵<br />\n做咁撚多仆街野<br />\n有無出黎道過歉？<br />\n打撚死人都唔道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以大家真係要檢討下，自己點樣支持前線<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">緊記be water<br />\n時突襲時突然退兵<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">保留最大實力本身已經係一種威脅</span><br />\n對家想我地呢3日all in?咁我就慢慢同你玩，有咁耐拖咁耐，總唔能夠日日唔開鐵日日唔開商場，全部都係錢黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講緊係&ldquo;全港經濟&ldquo;丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n最後：屯門撚，我希望下次同狗對峙時，可分10至20人出黎做一個小隊，係安全既情況下走下拆下啲輕鐵站，記得要拆路軌上個舊方型物體<br />\n我個fd係港鐵車長，有野想同你地講。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621927\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621927</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我愛大家<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"7e914863ee809633819f512e54cb858645b17927","tid":1623554,"uid":183776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:49:17.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"67e805d47d2c8fe21f1a627a86cd4497474703bd","tid":1623554,"uid":145730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:02:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63a261a41c986cb44c543d228a9a27f133ae502d","tid":1623554,"uid":52147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:05:19.000Z","msg":"同意，推"},{"pid":"67f2bd5effe6658dc05e17bc88587649a691372d","tid":1623554,"uid":146508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"d12b4f48e20ef074859042081f450b0f855f299f","tid":1623554,"uid":146508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f2bd5effe6658dc05e17bc88587649a691372d","tid":1623554,"uid":146508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:36:03.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:36:16.000Z","msg":"幫我推"},{"pid":"ec8cda449753a4e2c959fbd92c9ae989772b3d0e","tid":1623554,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:36:44.000Z","msg":"Solomon叫臨時政府收皮<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623561</a>"},{"pid":"4d00fb49da5388843951f3d0a8b042af960291fb","tid":1623554,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:38:50.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n認同 慢慢玩"},{"pid":"74f87ec444169f5cac1fe1de0be2d7373281b473","tid":1623554,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:39:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43555dfea1bb71278051254f8bededcec9a3254","tid":1623554,"uid":281960,"like"